theme_set(theme_ggdist() + theme(
  strip.background = element_blank(),
  plot.title = element_text(hjust = .5),
  axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 0, hjust = .5)
))

ggplot <-
  function(...)
    ggplot2::ggplot(...) +
  scale_color_brewer(palette = 'Set2') +
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = 'Set2')
stimuli <-
  rmvnorm(50, mean = c(.5, .3), sigma = matrix(c(4, 1, 1, 3), ncol = 2))

ggarrange(
  as_tibble(stimuli) %>%
    ggplot(., aes(x = V1, y = V2)) +
    geom_point(
      color = 'skyblue2',
      shape = 16,
      size = 2
    ) +
    xlab('') + ylab('') + theme(
      axis.text.x = element_blank(),
      axis.text.y = element_blank(),
      axis.ticks = element_blank()
    ),
  as_tibble(stimuli) %>%
    ggplot(., aes(x = V1, y = V2)) +
    geom_point(
      color = 'goldenrod1',
      shape = 16,
      size = 2
    ) +
    xlab('') + ylab('') + theme(
      axis.text.x = element_blank(),
      axis.text.y = element_blank(),
      axis.ticks = element_blank()
    ),
  as_tibble(stimuli) %>%
    ggplot(., aes(x = V1, y = V2)) +
    geom_point(
      color = 'skyblue2',
      shape = 17,
      size = 2
    ) +
        xlab('') + ylab('') + theme(
      axis.text.x = element_blank(),
      axis.text.y = element_blank(),
      axis.ticks = element_blank()
    ),
  as_tibble(stimuli) %>%
    ggplot(., aes(x = V1, y = V2)) +
    geom_point(
      color = 'goldenrod1',
      shape = 17,
      size = 2
    ) +
     xlab('') + ylab('') + theme(
      axis.text.x = element_blank(),
      axis.text.y = element_blank(),
      axis.ticks = element_blank()
    ),
  ncol = 4
)

data <- rep(
  crossing(
    color = c('blue', 'yellow'),
    mark = c('triangle', 'circle'),
    participant = paste0('P', seq(1, 30, by = 1))
  )) %>% 
  group_by(participant) %>%
  mutate(answer = rnorm(4, c(5, 3, 5, 6), c(.75, .6, .56, .61))) %>%
  arrange(participant)

data %>% 
  ggplot(., aes(x = interaction(mark, color), y = answer)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 10), breaks = seq(0, 10, by = 2)) +
  xlab('')

data %>% 
  ggplot(., aes(x = interaction(mark, color), y = answer)) +
  geom_point(color = 'gray30', alpha = .2) +
 # facet_grid(color ~ mark) + 
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 10), breaks = seq(0, 10, by = 2)) +
  xlab('')

data %>% 
  group_by(mark, color) %>%
  mean_qi(answer) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = interaction(mark, color))) +
  geom_bar(aes(y = answer), stat = 'identity', fill = 'gray60', width = .25) + 
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = .lower, ymax = .upper), width = 0.1, size = .75) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 10), breaks = seq(0, 10, by = 2)) +
  xlab('')

data %>% 
  group_by(mark, color) %>%
  mean_qi(answer) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = interaction(mark, color))) +
  geom_point(aes(y = answer)) + 
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = .lower, ymax = .upper), width = 0, size = .75) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 10), breaks = seq(0, 10, by = 2)) +
  xlab('')

data %>%

  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 10), breaks = seq(0, 10, by = 2)) +
  xlab('')

model <- lme(answer ~ color + mark, data=data, random = ~1|participant)
kable(anova(model))

data %>% 
  group_by(mark, color) %>%
  mean_qi(answer) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(y = interaction(mark, color))) +
  geom_point(aes(x = answer, color = color, shape = mark), size = 2) +
